I have one of these heaters in my 65 Kombi....   and this past summer I did
about 13000 miles from July untill about end of October- mid November...
many miles were with a friend of mine who is about 6'...   he didn't
complain about lack of leg room...

At first when I first bought the bus I wasn't too sure how I liked the
heater....   but now i have grown attached to it... not to mention how it
puts the heat right where you need it...  up front !!   It works great when
the cold weather comes....

