I have a Splitty under dash gas heater that I have never installed in my
bus.  I live in FL so it is not like I *really* need it except for the few
days a year it gets cold during the winter and a couple days during the
summer when I am on vacation in the mountains.  For the other 360 days I'm a
little worried about the amount of legroom it will take up.  Does anybody
have one of these installed who can tell me about how the passengers comfort
is effected?

